<!-- ==================== VIEW: GUIDE ==================== -->
<div id="view-guide" class="app-view active wrap">
  <header class="cover">
    <span class="blob b1"></span><span class="blob b2"></span>
    <div class="kicker">Grammar & Vocab</div>
    <h1>句子，是用积木搭起来的</h1>
    <p>——快速掌握长难句与核心词汇的终极训练营。懂了积木原理，阅读就像玩拼图！</p>
  </header>

  <div class="guide-card">
    <h2 class="font-zcool text-2xl mb-2">1. 核心积木理论</h2>
    <p>一句话不管多长，本质上只有三种积木：</p>
    <div class="blocks-demo">
      <div class="blk main">主菜<small>句子的核心，必不可少</small></div>
      <div class="blk clause">配菜 (从句)<small>补充说明：谁、什么</small></div>
      <div class="blk verb">配菜 (非谓语)<small>补充动作：怎么做、目的</small></div>
      <div class="blk prep">配菜 (介词)<small>补充细节：在哪里、何时</small></div>
      <div class="blk sign">路标词<small>连接词(and/so/when)</small></div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-sm text-[#6B6258] mt-3"><b>玩法：</b>找主菜，挑出配菜，圈出路标词。骨架一清二楚！</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mt-8">
    <div class="guide-card text-center" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <i class="fas fa-bolt text-4xl text-[#E8552B] mb-3"></i>
      <h3 class="font-zcool text-xl">词汇扫雷</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-5">包含文章中A2级别以上的核心生词，不认识的词汇将自动高频回炉。</p>
      <button onclick="switchTab('vocab')" class="action-btn-large" style="font-size:18px; padding:10px;">开始过单词</button>
    </div>
    <div class="guide-card text-center" style="margin-bottom:0;">
      <i class="fas fa-layer-group text-4xl text-[#2D7DD2] mb-3"></i>
      <h3 class="font-zcool text-xl">长难句拆解</h3>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-5">每天自动解锁新关卡，达到 <b>85%以上</b> 准确率也可提前解锁下一套。</p>
      <button onclick="navToSyntax()" class="action-btn-large" style="font-size:18px; padding:10px; background:#2D7DD2; border-color:#2D7DD2;">挑战拆句子</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

